ffects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/187153/', '', 'Meprobamate, Oxazepam', 'Azelastine', 1767369485);
